SVA2 Master Plan
================

o Critical Features
  o MMU
  x Zero out live registers in handlers.S
  o CFI check that we're jumping to a kernel-level address
  o Determine what is causing overhead and fix it
  o Get Apache to work
  o Test ssh-agent with ssh client
  o Add appendix
  o FP optimization

o SVA-OS
  o MMU
  x Process creation and deletion
    x kernel thread creation
    x process creation
    x process deletion
  x Invoke instructions
    x invoke
      x sva_invoke
      x sva_invokestrcpy
    x sva_iunwind
      x sva_invoke
      x sva_invokestrcpy
  x Signal handler dispatch
    x IC loading and saving
    x sva_ipush
    x sva_ialloca
  o Context Switching
    x Basic context switching
    x Adding page table register
    o FP optimzation
  x Interrupt Context
    x Zero out live registers
    x System Calls
    x Interrupts
    x Process creation/destruction
    x Floating point state
  o I/O
  o IPI Interrupts (2 weeks)

o Kernel
  x Enable ULE
  o Enable SMP

o Compiler Instrumentation
  o Control-Flow Integrity
    x Basic control-flow integrity
    o Check that we're jumping to a kernel-level address
    o Non-writable kernel code memory
    o Improve CFI callgraph
    o Enable CFI optimizations
  o SFI
    o MachineFunctionPass for Load/Store Instrumentation (3 weeks)

o Writing
  o Appendix
  o Fix Figure 2
  o Add std. dev. to Tables 3, 4, and 5

o Experiments
  o Get Apache to work
  o Get SLOC changes for FreeBSD kernel
  o Test ssh-agent with ssh client
  o Determine what is causing overhead and fix it

o Applications using Secure Memory (3 weeks)
  o Improve libghost wrapper library
  o Wrap thttpd or some other application

